Class: Java smartphone Mini 2 
Assignment 2: Mortgage App
Author: Wei-Lin Tsai weilints@andrew.cmu.edu
AndrewID: weilints

Info: 
    This is developmented by latest Android Studio. Please 
    use it to load it. 

Note:
    Flow:
    1. Get data when button is clicked.
    2. Query DB to see if existing record (See testdata/test_output.txt)
    3. Do calculation if there's no previous record. And then insert to DB
    4. Display the result in GUI

    PMI & ZIP code:
       We do not use these two field during calculation to simply the flow.

    Invalid Input:
       Will display error msg and do nothing. User can retype the input
       to get result again. Please see testdata/GUI_blank_input_result.png 

    Content in Mortgage/app/build is removed to reduce zip file.

Contents:
    README: This file
    
    Source code:
        Util: DB operation
        Mortgage/app/src/main/java/com/example/moumoutsay/mortgage/com/example/moumoutsay/mortgage/util/DBUtil.java
        Mortgage/app/src/main/java/com/example/moumoutsay/mortgage/com/example/moumoutsay/mortgage/util/SQLCmd.java
        Model: Mortgate calculation
        Mortgage/app/src/main/java/com/example/moumoutsay/mortgage/model/MortgageCal.java
        UI: Main activity
        Mortgage/app/src/main/java/com/example/moumoutsay/mortgage/ui/MainActivity.java

    Result 
